@startuml

title UC-6: Mark Course Task Complete
autonumber

actor "User" as U
boundary "Studently UI" as UI
database "DataStore" as DB
control "CourseService" as CourseSvc
entity "CourseTask" as CTask

U -> UI: Open Course → Open Task → Mark task as complete
UI -> CourseSvc: markTaskComplete(taskId)
CourseSvc -> DB: load(CTask)
CourseSvc -> CTask: markComplete()
note right
    Update progress within 500 ms (95%).
end note
CourseSvc -> DB: save(CTask)
DB --> CourseSvc: saved
CourseSvc --> UI: Show updated status (COMPLETE)

@enduml